16:32.390 --> 16:35.224
This is kind of creepy.

16:35.226 --> 16:37.059
We're not supposed to
talk during this part.

16:37.061 --> 16:39.795
Sorry.

16:45.603 --> 16:48.504
This is kind of creepy.

16:48.506 --> 16:50.272
Do you want to stop?

16:50.274 --> 16:52.174
I know you have trouble
with eye contact.

16:52.176 --> 16:55.578
Well, you have a brown fleck

16:55.580 --> 16:57.813
in your right iris that looks

16:57.815 --> 17:01.350
like a Formula One race car.

17:01.352 --> 17:05.387
So... I'm just
concentrating on that.

17:05.390 --> 17:08.958
Plus, it's easier around people
that I'm comfortable with.

17:08.960 --> 17:12.627
Aw, sweetie,
I'm comfortable around you, too.

17:12.630 --> 17:15.397
Of course you are,
I'm warm and soothing.

17:17.068 --> 17:19.969
I'm like a human bowl
of tomato soup.

17:19.971 --> 17:23.005
I meant more like
a little brother.

17:23.007 --> 17:25.040
Oh.

17:25.042 --> 17:28.109
Well, I suppose I do think
of you as a sister.

17:29.847 --> 17:32.615
And sometimes, a mother.

17:32.617 --> 17:34.717
It's getting creepy again.

17:42.927 --> 17:43.959
What?

17:43.961 --> 17:45.961
Just thinking about the day

17:45.963 --> 17:47.329
I met you and Leonard.

17:47.331 --> 17:49.098
It was a Monday afternoon.

17:49.100 --> 17:52.368
You joined us for Indian food.

17:52.370 --> 17:54.703
Can you believe
it's been eight years?

17:54.705 --> 17:57.807
Yeah, and you're
still eating our food.

18:01.112 --> 18:02.578
I... can't remember a time

18:02.580 --> 18:05.314
you guys weren't in my life.

18:05.316 --> 18:07.983
I remember it perfectly.

18:09.053 --> 18:11.554
But I have an eidetic memory.

18:11.556 --> 18:14.090
If you're interested,
I also remember

18:14.092 --> 18:17.026
how much you owe us
for the food.

18:20.665 --> 18:23.199
That's it.

18:23.201 --> 18:24.467
That wasn't so bad.

18:24.469 --> 18:25.668
No, it wasn't.

18:25.670 --> 18:27.336
Uh, now let's tabulate

18:27.338 --> 18:28.637
the results of the experiment.

18:28.639 --> 18:30.339
Okay.

18:30.341 --> 18:34.343
I think it's safe to say that
you're not in love with me

18:34.345 --> 18:36.245
and I'm not in love with you.

18:36.247 --> 18:38.881
And psychology has once again

18:38.883 --> 18:42.718
proved itself the doofus
of the sciences.

18:42.720 --> 18:45.087
Well, maybe.

18:45.089 --> 18:47.022
But I'm still glad we did it.

18:47.024 --> 18:49.558
I do feel closer to you.

18:49.560 --> 18:52.528
And I, you.

18:52.530 --> 18:55.664
And yes, that's
how you say that.

18:57.401 --> 19:00.803
Yeah, so, given our
newfound intimacy,

19:00.805 --> 19:02.371
I'd say we have

19:02.373 --> 19:03.873
some hard choices to make.

19:03.875 --> 19:04.974
Like what?

19:04.976 --> 19:08.344
Gary Con--
do we fly or drive?

19:08.346 --> 19:09.745
Do we wear costumes?

19:09.747 --> 19:11.947
And if so...

19:11.949 --> 19:14.884
who gets to be Gary?

19:23.484 --> 19:26.151
Thank you for walking me home.

19:26.153 --> 19:28.687
I just want to make sure
you get there safe.

19:30.084 --> 19:33.553
Well, this is me.

19:34.822 --> 19:36.756
It's been a very
interesting evening.

19:36.758 --> 19:38.391
It really has.

19:41.296 --> 19:43.095
Surprise!
Aah!

19:46.188 --> 19:48.433
And after I let you be Gary!

